</taxonomicName>
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="151">sp. nov.</emphasis>
Male imago: 1, general view, dorsal; 2, abdominal segments VIII-X, lateral view; 3, genitalia, ventral view. Nymph: 4, mature female nymph; 5, mature male nymph; 6, detail of head and pronotal coloration of not fully-grown male nymph.
</paragraph>
